#: .strings.ITEM_ANCIENT_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Upgrade one of your <style=cIsUtility>skills</style>. Reduce skill cooldown "
"by <style=cIsUtility>0%</style> <style=cStack>(+30% per stack. Unique per "
"survivor)</style>.\n"
"<style=cStack>Unusable pickups will reroll into other Legendary items.</"
"style>"
msgstr ""
"Покращує одну з ваших <style=cIsUtility>здібностей</style> "
"<style=cStack>(Унікально для кожного персонажа)</style>. Дає "
"<style=cIsUtility>+0%</style> <style=cStack>(+30% за кожен дублікат)</style> "
"до швидкості перезаряджання здібностей. \n"
"<style=cStack>У разі безкорисності, буде перетворено на інший легендарний "
"предмет.</style>"

#: .strings.ITEM_ANCIENT_SCEPTER_LORE
msgid ""
"Perfected energies. <He> holds it before us. The crystal of foreign elements "
"is not attached physically, yet it does not falter from the staff's "
"structure.\n"
"\n"
"Overwhelming strength. We watch as <His> might splits the ground asunder "
"with a single strike.\n"
"\n"
"Wondrous possibilities. <His> knowledge unlocks further pathways of "
"development. We are enlightened by <Him>.\n"
"\n"
"Excellent results. From <His> hands, [Nanga] takes hold. It is as <He> said: "
"The weak are culled.\n"
"\n"
"Risking everything. The crystal destabilizies. [Nanga] is gone, and <He> is "
"forced to wield it once again.\n"
"\n"
"Power comes at a cost. <He> is willing to pay."
msgstr ""
